QuestData.Title: Going West
QuestData.Description: Leza now walks with the ancestors of this strange land. I must look now to the living.$b$bKor has led a group of our scouts west deeper into the jungle.$b$bTrack him down and lend what aid you can to him. We will join you as quickly as we are able.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Kor Bloodtusk at Dawnchaser Retreat in the Krasarang Wilds.
